title: Art Workshop: Introduction to Watercolor Painting
desc: Join us for an engaging art workshop where you will learn the basics of watercolor painting. This workshop is perfect for beginners or those looking to brush up on their skills. Our experienced instructors will guide you through various techniques and help you create your own beautiful watercolor artwork. All materials will be provided, and no prior experience is required.
remark: Participants are advised to wear casual clothing that may get stained. Limited spots available, so book your tickets early.
presenterorg: Presented by Ap Lei Chau Public Library

title: Comedy Night: Laughter Therapy with Stand-Up Stars
desc: Get ready for a night of laughter as some of the funniest stand-up comedians take the stage at Black Box Theatre. This comedy extravaganza will have you rolling in the aisles with their hilarious jokes and witty observations. Join us for a dose of laughter therapy and leave with a smile on your face. Limited seats available, so book your tickets early!
remark: Please note that this event contains adult content and language. No photography or recording is allowed during the performance.
